    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到 Seclusa！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seclusa 是一款融合了休闲摄影模拟和舒适放置类型的游戏，你可以根据自己的喜好选择主动或被动的游戏方式。无论是拍摄当地的野生动物，还是在夕阳西下时于篝火旁放松身心，每个区域都经过精心设计，具有高度的氛围感，让人身临其境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116610/extras/eebedac5650cc69c8cc584a45d8bd65e.poster.avif?t=1771890825\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116610/extras/eebedac5650cc69c8cc584a45d8bd65e.webm?t=1771890825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116610/extras/eebedac5650cc69c8cc584a45d8bd65e.mp4?t=1771890825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拍摄照片</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好你的相机，在为若干保护组织完成摄影工作的过程中，拍摄各种东非野生动物。随着等级的提升，你将解锁更多的动物和地点，还能解锁相机升级，从而彻底改变照片的外观和风格。留意每个物种的稀有变种！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >获得经验值与升级</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成每日任务，达成目标，或者打开收音机，欣赏周围的自然风光，感受时光流逝。升级可以获得积分，用于改善相机、购买小屋设施、积累卡片收藏，甚至解锁能够随心所欲改变天气和时间的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116610/extras/132bd2c63592d08553ed339df9357968.poster.avif?t=1771890825\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116610/extras/132bd2c63592d08553ed339df9357968.webm?t=1771890825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116610/extras/132bd2c63592d08553ed339df9357968.mp4?t=1771890825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >摄影沙盒</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁所有功能后，你可以根据自己的喜好自由选择拍摄对象和场景。你可以改变时间和天气，调整照片的处理方式以适应氛围，还可以选择特定的物种作为拍摄对象。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >放松与减压</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seclusa 的设计理念是打造一个没有压力、以点击为主的体验，无论你喜欢主动还是被动的游戏方式，都可以舒适享受。无论你是在小屋里玩拼图游戏、打开收藏卡包，还是试图拍摄珍稀动物，都可以坐下来欣赏身临其境的非洲声音环境和原声音乐。祝你游戏愉快，尽情享受吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116610/extras/4bdd35e909d3d16c5eb38ef94e5f4c5b.poster.avif?t=1771890825\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116610/extras/4bdd35e909d3d16c5eb38ef94e5f4c5b.webm?t=1771890825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116610/extras/4bdd35e909d3d16c5eb38ef94e5f4c5b.mp4?t=1771890825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
